<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10675796>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Scanning electronic microscopy of male left palp, ventral view.A T. musica (Mello-Leitão, 1945) (MCN 53370). B T. quadripunctata (Mello-Leitão, 1944) (MCTP 16531). C T. yungae Galiano, 1970 (MCN 44133). D T. serrana Galiano, 1970 (MCTP 31126). E T. aisenbergae Marta, sp. nov. (IBSP 118477). F T. peniaflorensis Galiano, 1970 (FNAG36 1464). Scale bars: 0.50 mm. Colored homology: purple and purple arrow (tegular membranous process), blue (embolar base), green (conductor), magenta (tegulum), orange (embolus), red (pars pendula)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10675796/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10675802>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Expanded male left palp of Tullgrenella.A–C T. musica (Mello-Leitão, 1945) (MCN 53371), ventral (A), retrolateral (B) and prolateral (C) view. D–F T. lunata (Mello-Leitão, 1944) (MACN-Ar 42300), ventral view (D), retrolateral (E) and prolateral (F) view. G–I T. serrana Galiano, 1970 (MACN-Ar 6262), ventral (G), retrolateral (H) and prolateral (I) view. Scale bars: 0.50 mm. Black arrow: rotation direction; arrows in other colors refer to the structures with the same annotated colors." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10675802/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10675804>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Illustrations of female epigynum of Tullgrenella, dorsal view. A–E morenensis group: A T. morenensis (Tullgren, 1905) (MCN 19940), B T. guayapae Galiano, 1970 (MCN 55520), C T. brescoviti Estol, Marta & Rodrigues, 2020 (MCN 24104), D T. musica (Mello-Leitão,1945) (MCN 53372), E T. corrugata Galiano, 1981 (MACN-Ar 7206). F–H quadripunctata group: F T. quadripunctata (Mello-Leitão, 1944) (MCTP 2239), G T. nadjae Estol, Marta & Rodrigues, 2020 (MCN 56814), H T. lunata (Mello-Leitão, 1944) (MACN-Ar 6214). I–J melanica group: I T. melanica (Mello-Leitão, 1941) (MACN-Ar 6244), J T. yungae Galiano, 1970 (MCTP 39713). K–O serrana group: K T. serrana Galiano, 1970 (MCTP 12173), L T. legalissima Marta & Hagopián, sp. nov. (IBSP 118228), M T. aisenbergae Marta, sp. nov. (IBSP 123129), N T. gertschi Galiano, 1981 (MACN-Ar 7206), O T. sciosciae Marta & Bustamante, sp. nov. (MCTP 31135). P–Q peniaflorensis group: P T. peniaflorensis Galiano, 1970 (MACN-Ar 6242), Q T. selenita Galiano, 1970 (FNAC 36). Scale bars: 0.25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10675804/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10675884>
    dc:description "FIGURE 32. Photographs in vivo. A–D T. serrana Galiano, 1970:A–B female (FCE-Ar 11149), C–D male (FCE-Ar 9538). E–F female of T. legalissima Marta & Hagopián, sp. nov. (FCE-Ar 12155). Photographs by D. Hagopián." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10675884/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10675888>
    dc:description "FIGURE 33. Male of T. serrana Galiano, 1970 (MCN 46708). A habitus, dorsal view, red arrow: spotted coloration pattern. B same, ventral view. C left palp, ventral view, red arrow: tegulum central depression. D same, retrolateral view, red arrow: hook between RTA and prolatero-dorsal tibial apophysis, red dashed line: prolatero-dorsal tibial apophysis. Scale bars: A–B 1 mm, C–D 0.50 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10675888/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10675890>
    dc:description "FIGURE 34. Female of T. serrana Galiano, 1970 (MCTP 12173). A habitus, dorsal view, red arrow: spotted coloration pattern. B same, ventral view. C epigynum, ventral view. D same, dorsal view. Scale bars: A–B 1 mm, C–D 0.25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10675890/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10675912>
    dc:description "FIGURE 43. Scanning electronic microscopy of male palp, ventral view. A zoom of RTA of T. quadripunctata (Mello-Leitão, 1944) (MCTP 16531), white arrow: hook between RTA and prolatero-dorsal tibial apophysis, red arrow: lyriform organ. B zoom of RTA of T. serrana Galiano, 1970 (MCTP 31126), white arrow: hook between RTA and prolatero-dorsal tibial apophysis. C femur ventral projection of T. yungae Galiano, 1970 (MCN 44133), white arrow: projection. D femur ventral projection of T. aisenbergae Marta sp. nov. (IBSP 118477), white arrow: projection." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10675912/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10675934>
    dc:description "FIGURE 53. Neotropical andAndean regionalization (Morrone 2014) and distributional records for species of the serrana group. A Neotropical, South America, Brazilian subregion Chacoan subregion, South America Transition Zone and Andean region. B Southern South America, focusing on species occurrence. C habitat inference, URUGUAY: Sierra de Ríos, photographed by collector Damián Hagopián." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10675934/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

